1
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,480
Sun,

2
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,720
new brew today?

3
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,440
I've already eaten.

4
00:00:27,888 --> 00:00:28,560
Good grief.

5
00:00:28,590 --> 00:00:29,800
You never hear a word I say.

6
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:31,120
Have you eaten too?

7
00:00:33,410 --> 00:00:34,630
Steamed buns for sale!

8
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,400
Fresh out of the steamer!

9
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,610
Coming through.

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,600
(Wanyue Pavilion)
Come on in, sir.

11
00:00:54,620 --> 00:00:55,720
Come upstairs.

12
00:00:55,866 --> 00:00:56,860
(Flower Lanterns)
Sun.

13
00:00:56,870 --> 00:00:57,440
Yes?

14
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,150
This batch...

15
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:02,280
It's freshly brewed.

16
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,680
It's so strong.

17
00:01:06,710 --> 00:01:07,300
Oh.

18
00:01:07,340 --> 00:01:08,120
Unload the liquor.

19
00:01:08,155 --> 00:01:09,400
(Fuxian Restaurant)
Shopkeeper!

20
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,700
Four barrels of osmanthus liquor!

21
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,680
Good food and drink.

22
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,940
- There are exciting stories too!
- Sir.

23
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:15,990
- Keep eating.
- Inside, please.

24
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,560
(Drunken Moon Paradise)
Drink up.

25
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:18,840
Bring the liquor already!
Why is it taking so long?

26
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:20,155
Sorry to keep you waiting, sir.

27
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,160
Coming right up.

28
00:01:21,220 --> 00:01:22,670
Fine brew is worth the wait.

29
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,430
I've waited so long.
There's still no liquor?

30
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,330
Go on drinking.

31
00:01:25,380 --> 00:01:26,622
Hurry and bring the liquor.

32
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,190
This is heavy.

33
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,960
There should be more.

34
00:01:47,450 --> 00:01:48,560
Darned Sun.

35
00:01:48,688 --> 00:01:50,120
He never rinses his barrels properly.

36
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,730
What is this?

37
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:13,020
=The Tang Mist S1=

38
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:33,660
=Episode 12=

39
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:36,340
(Changsha)

40
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,320
Sir,

41
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,420
it's noon.

42
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,660
(Zhou Quan, Prefect of Tanzhou)

43
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:47,177
(Cui Junmao,
Magistrate of Changsha County)

44
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:49,750
Should've arrived by now.

45
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:51,980
What's going on?

46
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,800
No signs of struggle

47
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,920
inside the barrel.

48
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,130
No abdominal fill.

49
00:04:16,533 --> 00:04:18,355
The body was placed in the barrel
after death.

50
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,480
There are cuts all over the body.

51
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,550
I'm still searching for the fatal wound.

52
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:28,610
These scraps of flesh

53
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,480
were left behind after soaking.

54
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:34,930
Oh, sir.

55
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,400
Great Lord of Justice!

56
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:38,160
This has nothing to do with us.

57
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,250
The liquor

58
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:41,360
was delivered by Sun earlier today.

59
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:44,300
Lady Yue.

60
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,280
Sir,

61
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,500
I'm innocent!

62
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,360
It must be

63
00:04:50,410 --> 00:04:51,800
the fox demon again.

64
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,240
A fox demon?

65
00:04:55,370 --> 00:04:56,260
Move aside!

66
00:04:57,220 --> 00:04:58,530
Who has such audacity

67
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,920
to barge into a crime scene?

68
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,000
Take them all away!

69
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,760
Hush.

70
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,080
Quiet down.

71
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,840
We're examining the body. Keep it down.

72
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:05,800
Who are you?

73
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,160
Who are you people?

74
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,840
Do you have no regard for the law?

75
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:12,320
- Do you have no...
- Shut your mouth!

76
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,822
This is Imperial Commissioner
of Jiangnan,

77
00:05:16,933 --> 00:05:18,000
Di Renjie.

78
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,120
Well...

79
00:05:20,490 --> 00:05:21,480
Di Renjie

80
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,080
is sent by the Heavenly Empress.

81
00:05:23,444 --> 00:05:24,933
We can't afford to slight him.

82
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,360
We'll wait

83
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:27,980
until he arrives.

84
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:30,920
But another fox demon murder happened
in the county this morning.

85
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,430
The victim was a bureau runner.

86
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,440
How about...

87
00:05:34,666 --> 00:05:36,066
Which do you think takes priority?

88
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:38,520
Wait.

89
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,488
Wait until he arrives.

90
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,800
Sir!

91
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,000
Sir!

92
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:44,533
Di Renjie is at Fuxian Restaurant now!

93
00:05:44,540 --> 00:05:46,210
Captain Cai almost
got into a fight with him.

94
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:46,680
What?

95
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,040
Magistrate Cui,

96
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,280
what's your problem?

97
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,000
Buyan,

98
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,950
sketch the wounds.

99
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,800
Yes, Master.

100
00:05:58,911 --> 00:06:00,520
We waited at the city gate
since dawn

101
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,160
for your arrival, Commissioner Di.

102
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,190
But we didn't catch sight of you.

103
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,800
Turns out

104
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,840
you'd already entered the city.

105
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,530
No wonder.

106
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:10,740
You didn't show up

107
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,920
at the crime scene.

108
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,040
I almost thought

109
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,160
there were no officials of Tang here.

110
00:06:16,533 --> 00:06:17,422
I'm Cui Junmao, sir.

111
00:06:17,444 --> 00:06:19,270
Multiple murders have occurred
under my jurisdiction.

112
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,480
I've failed in my duty.

113
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,920
Please forgive me, Commissioner Di.

114
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,480
Take those who drank the blood liquor

115
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,520
to get treated.

116
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,800
The bureau will cover

117
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:30,160
all the medical expenses.

118
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:30,630
Yes, sir.

119
00:06:30,710 --> 00:06:31,350
Yes, sir.

120
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,520
Hurry.

121
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,560
Get them all out of here.

122
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,360
I failed

123
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:38,700
to discipline my subordinate.

124
00:06:38,777 --> 00:06:40,200
Please forgive me, Commissioner Di.

125
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,680
Perhaps you should eat first

126
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,480
and rest from your travels.

127
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,570
The Great Tang

128
00:06:48,822 --> 00:06:50,050
is a land governed by the law,

129
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:52,780
yet a bureau runner
was brazenly murdered

130
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:54,040
in broad daylight,

131
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:57,760
while the rumor of a fox demon killing
is making the rounds among the people.

132
00:06:58,333 --> 00:06:59,550
What do you make of this,

133
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,990
Prefect?

134
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:11,880
Commissioner Di,

135
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,240
I'm aware of that.

136
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,800
It really was a fox demon.

137
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,680
The previous victim was Pisi.

138
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,440
He was a broker.

139
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:20,288
A few days ago,
Pisi was traveling on business.

140
00:07:20,288 --> 00:07:21,622
On his way down the mountain,

141
00:07:21,711 --> 00:07:23,390
he passed an abandoned house
in the woods.

142
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,360
Young Lady,

143
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,580
I'm thirsty.

144
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,640
Could I ask for a bowl of water?

145
00:07:28,020 --> 00:07:28,760
Not long after,

146
00:07:28,866 --> 00:07:30,866
a terrible stench
came from inside the house.

147
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,670
A passing beggar
reported it to the authorities.

148
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,290
Captain,

149
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,130
over there.

150
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,480
Pisi died horribly.

151
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,320
His face was clawed open.

152
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,960
Those were clearly beast marks.

153
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,120
And his heart was ripped out.

154
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,720
If that wasn't a fox demon,

155
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,550
what else could it be, sir?

156
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,290
Enough.

157
00:08:01,330 --> 00:08:02,200
Stop talking now.

158
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,280
The body is stiff.

159
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,200
Lividity has formed.

160
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,760
The eyes are slightly clouded.

161
00:08:13,822 --> 00:08:15,680
The time of death
was around twelve hours ago.

162
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,040
Late Hai hour last night.

163
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:20,360
Sir, the corpse bears
eleven major wounds.

164
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,630
At the preliminary examination,
they resemble claw marks

165
00:08:22,644 --> 00:08:23,960
of beasts.

166
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,600
The cuts are deep,

167
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,400
but none of them are fatal.

168
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,080
Chest.

169
00:08:36,680 --> 00:08:37,600
He died

170
00:08:38,511 --> 00:08:39,800
because his heart was dug out.

171
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,800
Again?

172
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:43,480
This is terrifying.

173
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,220
It has to be a fox demon.

174
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,240
Magistrate Cui,

175
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:48,680
within two hours, investigate

176
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:51,880
the movements of Xu Da and Pisi
over the past month.

177
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,280
Find the witnesses.

178
00:08:53,290 --> 00:08:55,022
Verify the times and locations
of the murders.

179
00:08:55,044 --> 00:08:55,511
Yes, sir.

180
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,320
Captain,

181
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:58,240
tighten security at all city gates.

182
00:08:58,450 --> 00:08:59,410
All ingress and egress

183
00:08:59,450 --> 00:09:00,360
must be recorded.

184
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,400
Yes, sir.

185
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,480
Qinglan,

186
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,770
reexamine both bodies thoroughly.

187
00:09:04,844 --> 00:09:05,444
Yes, sir.

188
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,280
Whose mongrel is barking

189
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,720
on my turf?

190
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:14,660
(Li Qian, Lord Xunjiang)

191
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:15,940
Are you blind...

192
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,030
Hush.

193
00:09:18,050 --> 00:09:19,733
This isn't someone you can mess with.

194
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,880
I, Di Renjie, greet Lord Xunjiang.

195
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,200
Commissioner Di,

196
00:09:31,311 --> 00:09:33,640
you wave the Heavenly Empress's decree
around on my land

197
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,760
like your own place.

198
00:09:36,090 --> 00:09:36,800
I almost thought

199
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:38,480
you had forgotten

200
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,120
there's a Lord Xunjiang in Tanzhou.

201
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,600
Your Lordship,

202
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,290
I certainly am aware of that.

203
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,830
But court affairs are piling up,

204
00:09:46,955 --> 00:09:48,666
and now Tanzhou has been plagued

205
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:49,830
by the fox demon killings.

206
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,840
The murders are gruesome.

207
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,840
I imagine

208
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:54,470
Your Lordship must be concerned
for the people

209
00:09:54,666 --> 00:09:55,880
and unable to sleep at night.

210
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,880
I merely wish to ease your worries

211
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:01,710
and restore peace to Tanzhou
as soon as possible.

212
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,600
That is why

213
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:05,066
I neglected property courtesy

214
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,480
and failed to pay my respects first.

215
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,880
Smooth talker.

216
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,440
What a loyal mutt
of the Heavenly Empress.

217
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,320
I've underestimated you.

218
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,440
Di Renjie,

219
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,000
I give you

220
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,720
three days

221
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,800
to solve the fox demon case.

222
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,200
If not,

223
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,300
get out of Tanzhou.

224
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,000
Yes, Your Lordship.

225
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,640
If the Li imperial family
had fewer fools like him,

226
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,600
things would never have come to this.

227
00:11:05,266 --> 00:11:06,550
(Fuxian Restaurant)
The liquor

228
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,640
was freshly brewed.

229
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,520
Commissioner Di asks

230
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,880
when the liquor was loaded

231
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,640
into the barrels.

232
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,560
Ah!

233
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:15,640
Commissioner Di,

234
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,320
it was filled around noon

235
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,622
before moving to the backyard.

236
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,160
We loaded them onto the donkey cart
this morning

237
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,560
(Fuxian Restaurant)
and sent them to Fuxian Restaurant.

238
00:11:22,090 --> 00:11:24,470
Did you stop anywhere along the way?

239
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,320
Commissioner Di is asking

240
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,480
if you made any stops.

241
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,000
Commissioner Di,

242
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,760
I came straight there.

243
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,850
None of you noticed

244
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,760
there was a body inside?

245
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,360
Uh...

246
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,360
Commissioner Di,

247
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,360
the two of us loaded the cart that day.

248
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:41,800
I did notice

249
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,760
one of the barrels

250
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,440
felt heavier than usual.

251
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:45,330
Oh, right!

252
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:46,080
I thought

253
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,720
he was slacking off,

254
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,840
so I argued with him over it.

255
00:11:49,170 --> 00:11:50,440
Right!

256
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,000
Master was rushing us that day,

257
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,600
so we didn't think much of it.

258
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,520
Commissioner Di,

259
00:11:54,770 --> 00:11:56,080
we honestly didn't kill anyone.

260
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:56,630
That's right!

261
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,810
This has nothing to do with us.

262
00:11:57,820 --> 00:11:59,480
- We swear it!
- We didn't kill him!

263
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:01,560
The killer must've known
Su was hard of hearing,

264
00:12:01,622 --> 00:12:03,600
which is why the victim was lured there.

265
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,360
Um...

266
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,520
Pisi died five days ago.

267
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,880
His heart was missing as well.

268
00:12:14,066 --> 00:12:15,911
The body had been boiled
beyond recognition.

269
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,711
The murder weapon can't be determined.

270
00:12:17,888 --> 00:12:19,777
There are no other useful clues for now.

271
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,680
Master,

272
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,720
look at their scarred faces.

273
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,320
Foxes love to eat hearts.

274
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,133
Could there really be a fox demon?

275
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,200
Young lad,

276
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:30,100
you've studied under your master
for years,

277
00:12:30,130 --> 00:12:32,240
and you're still so clueless?

278
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:34,560
Demons do not exist.

279
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,480
Sir, don't dismiss it so quickly.

280
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,755
There was a fox demon
in Ji'an Village two years ago.

281
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,440
Several people

282
00:12:39,490 --> 00:12:40,470
were eaten back then.

283
00:12:40,530 --> 00:12:41,480
Two years ago?

284
00:12:42,444 --> 00:12:43,940
Did you see it with your own eyes?

285
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:45,040
No, we didn't.

286
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,270
Someone did.

287
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,400
Who?

288
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,040
Magistrate Cui.

289
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:54,020
(Two Years Ago)

290
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,360
Two years ago,

291
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,200
I had just taken office
in Huarong County.

292
00:12:59,533 --> 00:13:02,422
While passing near Ji'an Village,
I came across a run-down temple.

293
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,440
It was bitterly cold,

294
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,720
so I sought shelter inside
from the storm.

295
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,260
You're a skilled painter.

296
00:13:12,650 --> 00:13:14,120
I wonder if

297
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:16,360
I'm worthy of a painting from you.

298
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,970
To paint such beauty

299
00:13:19,660 --> 00:13:21,080
is my great fortune.

300
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,840
Receiving a painting from you

301
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,800
on a snowy night

302
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,960
truly delights me.

303
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,240
It's only a painting.

304
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,840
You needn't take it to heart.

305
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,440
And if

306
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,200
I asked for

307
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,080
your heart,

308
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,520
would you grant my wish?

309
00:13:58,533 --> 00:14:00,333
I witnessed that with my own eyes.

310
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:03,250
After that, the fox demon began
killing people in the village.

311
00:14:03,333 --> 00:14:04,440
It was too bizarre,

312
00:14:04,850 --> 00:14:06,240
so I never dared tell anyone

313
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:08,060
about finding the painting.

314
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,850
Magistrate Cui,

315
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,440
are you telling me a ghost story?

316
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,800
Every word is true.

317
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,160
I would never dare deceive you.

318
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,880
Is there a case file on it?

319
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,960
There is, Commissioner Di.

320
00:14:30,244 --> 00:14:31,860
(Case Record)
(According to the files,)

321
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:36,400
(Two years ago, a fox demon
caused havoc in Ji'an Village.)

322
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:38,933
(Chen Sheng)
(Chen Sheng, a passing scholar)

323
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:39,970
(died tragically.)

324
00:14:40,560 --> 00:14:42,770
(This incident was witnessed by
Magistrate Cui.)

325
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:45,880
(Later, a traveling physician
named Zhuo Ji)

326
00:14:46,070 --> 00:14:47,450
(was killed.)

327
00:14:47,511 --> 00:14:50,088
(It cemented the belief
that the fox demon was killing people.)

328
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:52,800
(Villagers of Ji'an fled in fear)

329
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,480
(and abandoned the village.)

330
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,160
(From then on, Ji'an Village)

331
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,230
(was left deserted.)

332
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:07,310
Mother!

333
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:09,320
Mother, save me!

334
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,910
Mother!

335
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,810
- Mother!
- Fu'an!

336
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:15,220
- Fu'an!
- Mother!

337
00:15:30,140 --> 00:15:31,820
Master, the bureau just sent word.

338
00:15:31,911 --> 00:15:33,266
The fox demon has killed again.

339
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,720
The victim is a newlywed bride.

340
00:16:08,088 --> 00:16:09,955
It's Old Madam Jiang from South Alley!

341
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,040
(The wounds on the victim's body)

342
00:16:19,330 --> 00:16:21,170
(do resemble beast claws.)

343
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,840
(But the marks on the wooden chair)

344
00:16:29,770 --> 00:16:31,400
(and the scratches on the barrel)

345
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:33,120
(were made by sharp edges.)

346
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,850
(The cuts are clean)

347
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,320
(and even.)

348
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,760
(These were man-made.)

349
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,000
Did you find anything?

350
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,040
Flesh craps.

351
00:17:21,688 --> 00:17:24,080
Why were these found under
all three victims' fingernails?

352
00:17:25,822 --> 00:17:28,022
Could they have struggled
with the killer?

353
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:29,410
No.

354
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:30,733
Look, these wounds match

355
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:32,760
the width of their own fingernails.

356
00:17:32,933 --> 00:17:34,822
It's more like
they scratched themselves.

357
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,266
Let's go and see Commissioner Di.

358
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,040
Compare the wounds.

359
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,200
They match the cuts exactly.

360
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:57,920
Sir,

361
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,800
Xu Da's body was soaked in liquor.

362
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,680
The smell changed

363
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:01,680
and cannot be confirmed.

364
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,720
But shaqianzi were found

365
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:04,200
in the wounds on Pisi's face

366
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,360
and Old Madam Jiang's skin.

367
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:07,610
Shaqianzi?

368
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:09,090
It's known as a medicinal herb,

369
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:10,300
but it's rarely used in medicine.

370
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:11,440
It's more like a poison.

371
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:13,040
Colorless and odorless.

372
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:14,680
But once heavily applied to the skin,

373
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:15,880
body heat melts it

374
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,840
and releases a sweet fragrance.

375
00:18:17,850 --> 00:18:19,240
That scent attracts swarms of insects,

376
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,470
making the victim slowly suffocate

377
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:21,360
and unable to cry out.

378
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:22,890
We also found

379
00:18:23,210 --> 00:18:26,040
fresh scraps under
all three victims' fingernails.

380
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,680
I doubt they scratched themselves.

381
00:18:35,340 --> 00:18:37,540
(Pisi)

382
00:18:49,460 --> 00:18:52,380
(Xu Da)

383
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:56,240
First, the victims were drugged,
causing them to scratch themselves.

384
00:18:56,577 --> 00:18:58,244
Then one body was soaked in liquor,

385
00:18:58,310 --> 00:18:59,080
the other boiled,

386
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:01,644
while the rainstorm helped cover up
the scent of the poison.

387
00:19:01,666 --> 00:19:04,270
Finally, razor cuts were added
to fake claw wounds,

388
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:05,380
and the hearts were removed.

389
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:08,160
So this is the true color
of the so-called fox demon.

390
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:10,150
The murderer went to great lengths

391
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:11,600
to imitate fox demon killings.

392
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,400
But why?

393
00:19:13,050 --> 00:19:14,770
If we want to find out the motive,

394
00:19:15,044 --> 00:19:16,480
we must first uncover the connection

395
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:18,560
between the three victims.

396
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:24,410
Sir,

397
00:19:24,650 --> 00:19:26,280
Pisi and Xu Da had no family.

398
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:28,222
Only Old Madam Jiang
and her foolish son, Fu'an,

399
00:19:28,230 --> 00:19:29,466
depended on each other to survive.

400
00:19:29,533 --> 00:19:31,140
(Old Madam Jiang's House)

401
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:33,520
Examine the scene carefully.

402
00:19:33,520 --> 00:19:34,840
Leave no stone unturned.

403
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,420
Bad man.

404
00:19:37,020 --> 00:19:38,330
Fu'an, don't run around.

405
00:19:40,390 --> 00:19:42,240
You're all bad people.

406
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:52,900
It was raining yesterday.

407
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:54,790
The ground was muddy.

408
00:19:55,288 --> 00:19:57,133
If Old Madam Jiang were taken by force,

409
00:19:57,520 --> 00:19:58,960
at her age,

410
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:01,050
there would be signs of struggle.

411
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,560
There are only footprints here,

412
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:06,930
and no signs of resistance at all.

413
00:20:07,030 --> 00:20:08,410
You're all bad people.

414
00:20:08,450 --> 00:20:09,280
That means the victim

415
00:20:09,330 --> 00:20:11,200
was either taken unconscious.

416
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:14,770
Or taken away by someone she knew.

417
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:16,560
Master.

418
00:20:17,533 --> 00:20:18,840
We've questioned the neighbors.

419
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,320
No one heard anything unusual.

420
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:21,400
But someone said

421
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:22,470
they heard

422
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:24,240
Fu'an frantically shaking
his rattle drum.

423
00:20:24,950 --> 00:20:25,840
Go away!

424
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:29,120
Bad man!

425
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,280
He's a bad man!

426
00:20:38,580 --> 00:20:39,720
An official uniform...

427
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:43,220
Xu Da.

428
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,570
Buyan.

429
00:20:50,730 --> 00:20:51,870
Is this the bad man?

430
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:54,460
Bad man!

431
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:55,970
Go away!

432
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:02,880
What did this bad man do?

433
00:21:03,120 --> 00:21:05,040
I can't say.

434
00:21:05,280 --> 00:21:05,960
Tell us.

435
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:07,040
I can't say.

436
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:09,120
Stop pushing him.

437
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:14,360
What did Xu Da do

438
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:15,880
in this woodshed?

439
00:21:19,990 --> 00:21:20,650
Di, this is

440
00:21:20,690 --> 00:21:23,520
the detailed record of Xu Da's
movements over the past month.

441
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:24,600
(Shen hour, money house)

442
00:21:24,688 --> 00:21:26,580
(13th, Shen hour, He Pawnshop)

443
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:27,660
Why would a bureau runner

444
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:29,560
frequent a pawnshop?

445
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:31,240
Look into it.

446
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:31,900
Yes.

447
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:52,320
Sir,

448
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:54,200
I've reexamined all three corpses.

449
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,200
No traces of sedatives.

450
00:21:55,210 --> 00:21:57,044
No knockout powder
was found in their stomach either.

451
00:21:57,045 --> 00:21:59,550
The most likely possibility is
that the killer was someone they knew.

452
00:22:00,570 --> 00:22:01,970
No one heard anything unusual.

453
00:22:02,010 --> 00:22:02,980
But someone said

454
00:22:03,010 --> 00:22:03,700
they heard

455
00:22:03,730 --> 00:22:05,520
Fu'an frantically shaking
his rattle drum.

456
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:08,220
On the night Old Madam Jiang died,

457
00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:09,760
Fu'an probably saw

458
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:12,670
the killer.

459
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:14,660
(Preview of Next Episode)

460
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,640
Finish this.

461
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:17,840
Grow up big and strong,

462
00:22:17,950 --> 00:22:19,620
so you can give me a strong grandson.

463
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:22,960
I said eat!

464
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:23,960
You won't eat?

465
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:25,560
Eat!

466
00:22:25,760 --> 00:22:26,800
Eat it!

467
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:28,760
Hurry up and eat!

468
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:29,860
Easy.

469
00:22:43,190 --> 00:22:44,770
♪Night covers the long streets♪

470
00:22:45,850 --> 00:22:47,560
♪The city remains silent♪

471
00:22:48,950 --> 00:22:50,540
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

472
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:53,040
♪Words still left unspoken♪

473
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:56,080
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

474
00:22:57,210 --> 00:22:59,680
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

475
00:23:00,300 --> 00:23:01,780
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

476
00:23:01,780 --> 00:23:04,920
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

477
00:23:05,540 --> 00:23:07,460
♪Love is born from desire♪

478
00:23:08,150 --> 00:23:10,280
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

479
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:13,080
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

480
00:23:13,080 --> 00:23:16,380
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

481
00:23:17,830 --> 00:23:19,150
♪Someone once warned me♪

482
00:23:19,150 --> 00:23:20,670
♪To stop upon this shore♪

483
00:23:20,670 --> 00:23:21,990
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

484
00:23:21,990 --> 00:23:23,480
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

485
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,600
♪If one thought retreats♪

486
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:25,900
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

487
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:27,240
♪But in this world♪

488
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,640
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

489
00:23:31,470 --> 00:23:34,280
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

490
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:35,750
♪Still I walk ahead♪

491
00:23:35,980 --> 00:23:37,200
♪Let it pierce through♪

492
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:41,940
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

493
00:23:41,940 --> 00:23:44,180
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

494
00:23:44,180 --> 00:23:45,580
♪Covering every heart♪

495
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:46,770
♪How many people♪

496
00:23:47,030 --> 00:23:48,400
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

497
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,610
♪Yet call it♪

498
00:23:50,810 --> 00:23:52,150
♪Fate?♪

499
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:53,690
♪Life and death♪

500
00:23:53,690 --> 00:23:54,950
♪Balanced on a single line♪

501
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:56,470
♪Light and shadow♪

502
00:23:56,470 --> 00:23:57,730
♪Hanging side by side♪

503
00:23:57,730 --> 00:23:59,210
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

504
00:23:59,210 --> 00:24:00,620
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

505
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:02,160
♪In the end, it is only♪

506
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,540
♪A single misguided thought♪

507
00:24:03,540 --> 00:24:05,100
♪If unveiling the truth♪

508
00:24:05,100 --> 00:24:06,440
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

509
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,610
♪Then this answer♪

510
00:24:07,610 --> 00:24:08,970
♪Can it still remain true?♪

511
00:24:08,970 --> 00:24:10,370
♪When love and law♪

512
00:24:10,370 --> 00:24:11,850
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

513
00:24:11,850 --> 00:24:13,250
♪Which figure before me♪

514
00:24:13,250 --> 00:24:20,450
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

515
00:24:20,450 --> 00:24:23,180
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

516
00:24:23,180 --> 00:24:24,770
♪Still I walk ahead♪

517
00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:26,010
♪Not for fame or glory♪

518
00:24:26,010 --> 00:24:30,880
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

519
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,690
♪Human nature is clouded♪

520
00:24:32,690 --> 00:24:34,410
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

521
00:24:34,410 --> 00:24:35,880
♪Though this world♪

522
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,250
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

523
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:39,500
♪There is still a light♪

524
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:42,460
♪Worth pursuing♪

525
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:44,280
♪Every case has its ending♪

526
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:45,540
♪But night does not always fade♪

527
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:47,190
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

528
00:24:47,190 --> 00:24:48,410
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

529
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:49,760
♪If justice stands♪

530
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:51,010
♪Without mercy beside it♪

531
00:24:51,010 --> 00:24:52,810
♪Then how is it♪

532
00:24:52,810 --> 00:25:02,370
♪Any different from a blade?♪

533
00:25:02,370 --> 00:25:05,560
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

534
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:07,040
♪Still I walk ahead♪

535
00:25:07,040 --> 00:25:08,430
♪Even if the world♪

536
00:25:08,430 --> 00:25:13,160
♪Refuses to answer♪

537
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:15,120
♪When every hidden truth♪

538
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,830
♪Finally reveals itself♪

539
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:18,190
♪I only wish♪

540
00:25:18,190 --> 00:25:19,670
♪To hold on♪

541
00:25:19,670 --> 00:25:24,410
♪Within the darkness♪

542
00:25:24,410 --> 00:25:26,410
♪To the heart♪

